short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays manual Test Results attachments in larger view and allows printing of test results.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: In Microsoft Azure DevOps, this extension modifies the page CSS attributes to display manual Test Results attachments in a larger format for viewing in the browser window.  Allows printing of just test results from the test results page.
